{{Wireless embedded system |brand=Belkin |model=F7D7602 |revision=v1 |manuf_country=China |is_manuf=No |manuf= |fcc_date=03/19/2013 |fcc_id=K7SF7D7602V1 |ic_id=3623A-F7D7602V1 |pcb_id=75053503 |type=camera |pwr_v=5 |pwr_amp=1 |pwr_conn=barrel |cpu1_brand=Ralink |cpu1_model=RT5350 |cpu2_brand=AIT |cpu2_model=AIT8431T |fla1=16 |fla1_brand=Winbond |fla1_model=W25Q128FVSG |ram1=64 |ram1_brand=Winbond |ram1_model=W9825G6JH-6 |ram1_num=2 |wi1_chip1_brand=Ralink |wi1_chip1_model=RT5350 |wi1_802dot11_protocols=bgn |wi1_txchains=1 |wi1_rxchains=1 |wi1_sstreams=1 |eth_cpu=true |lan_speed=100M |lan_ports=1 |addl_chips=Multimedia Processor;AIT;AIT8431T;;1; ,,, Mono Audio Codec;Nuvoton;NAU8810YG;;1; |802dot11_protocols=bgn |default_ssid=NetCamHDXXXX |default_ssid_regex=^NetCamHD[A-F0-9]{4}$ |oui=EC:1A:59 }} {{TagLine|NetCam HD}}
"75053503", "2013-01-17", and "REV1.0" is silkscreened :on the board in the FCC photos.
Also per the FCC photos, this device is using... *[[Ralink]] RT5350 802.11bgn 1T1R WiSoC *''[[Winbond]]'' W25Q128FVSG (25Q128FVSG) 16MB Flash chip *2x ''[[Winbond]]'' W9825G6JH-6 (32MB each, 64MB total) RAM *an ''[[AIT]]'' AIT8431T Multimedia Processor *a ''[[Nuvoton]]'' NAU8810YG Mono Audio Codec
Per the FCC label and the example label in the external photos... *the device has a default setup SSID pattern of '''NetCamHDXXXX''' :(where '''XXXX''' appears to be the last 4 digits of the wireless :interface MAC [upper case letters]) *the device will use a EC:1A:59 OUI
